this  expriment  was  done  on  a wooden  plank 

exprimental setup
  materials :  a  top plate( wooden  plank)  supported  by two risers (smaller  wooden planks)  , a  breadboard condating  accloromeater  and nodemcu    attached  to  the small setup

 connections:  plate and risers  are connected  with super glue(ca glue)   ,  the  small breadboard  has   a tape  on its bottom  by which it  was  connected to   
